"title": "6028: sin, God's deliverance from",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6028",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel reveals the purpose and power of God to deal with sin and all of its effects. Scripture uses a range of images to express the comprehensiveness of salvation.</p>\n<h2>God's removal of sin</h2>\n<h3>Atonement for sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:7\">ISA 6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:30\">EXO 32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev4:27-Lev4:31\">LEV 4:27–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:6\">PRO 16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25\">ROM 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">HEB 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Forgiveness of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18\">MIC 7:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38\">ACT 13:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:35-1Kgs8:36\">1KI 8:35–8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:18-2Chr30:20\">2CH 30:18–30:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:2-Ps103:3\">PSA 103:2–103:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:24\">ISA 33:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:7\">ISA 55:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:21\">JOL 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:27-Matt26:28\">MAT 26:27–26:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:47\">LUK 24:46–24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:7\">EPH 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Cancellation of a debt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:12\">MAT 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:41-Luke7:50\">LUK 7:41–7:50</a></p>\n<h3>A covering over of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:8\">1PE 4:8</a></strong> <em>There is a close relation between “covering over sin” and “atoning for sin”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:1\">PSA 32:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:2\">PSA 85:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:20\">JAS 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>The taking away of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:12\">PSA 103:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13\">2SA 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:6-Isa6:7\">ISA 6:6–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:4\">ZEC 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:29\">JHN 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:5\">1JN 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Remembering sin no more</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:25\">ISA 43:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:7\">PSA 25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">JER 31:33–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19\">2CO 5:19</a></p>\n<h2>God's deliverance for the sinner</h2>\n<h3>The salvation of the sinner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:8-Ps28:9\">PSA 28:8–28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:9-Luke19:10\">LUK 19:9–19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:17\">JHN 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></p>\n<h3>The image of healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:31-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:31–5:32</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:12\">MAT 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:17\">MRK 2:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:18-Isa57:19\">ISA 57:18–57:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:4\">HOS 14:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></p>\n<h3>The image of cleansing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:2\">PSA 51:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:30\">LEV 16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:25\">EZK 36:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1-John13:11\">JHN 13:1–13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:16\">ACT 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Redemption by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:8\">PSA 130:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:22\">ISA 44:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:14\">TIT 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Justification before God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:16\">GAL 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:11\">ISA 53:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:24-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:24–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:5\">ROM 4:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:25\">ROM 4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:16-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:16–5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a></p>\n<h3>Freedom from condemnation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1\">ROM 8:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18\">JHN 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:11\">JHN 8:3–8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a></p>\n<h3>Peace with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1\">ROM 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:5\">ISA 53:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:14\">LUK 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17\">EPH 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Reconciliation with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:18\">2CO 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9-Rom5:11\">ROM 5:9–5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:19-Col1:20\">COL 1:19–1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Sanctification to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:26\">EPH 5:25–5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:22\">COL 1:22</a></p>\n<h3>Freedom from sin and the sinful nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24\">ROM 7:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:1-Rom6:18\">ROM 6:1–6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:9\">ROM 8:1–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:24\">GAL 5:24</a></p>\n<h3>A transition from death to life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:22-Luke15:24\">LUK 15:22–15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h3>Receiving eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></p>",
